ax-w-3xl leading-7 text-ink/72\">PageCub shapes those details into a gentle chapter book with a beginning, challenge, heart, and ending.</p></div></section><section class=\"grid gap-5 rounded-[2rem] border border-line bg-card p-7 shadow-sm md:grid-cols-[5rem_1fr]\"><span class=\"flex h-16 w-16 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-honey/30 text-2xl font-bold\">3</span><div><h2 class=\"display text-3xl font-bold\">Review the result</h2><p class=\"mt-3 max-w-3xl leading-7 text-ink/72\">You can see the finished book before ordering any printed copy.</p></div></section><section class=\"grid gap-5 rounded-[2rem] border border-line bg-card p-7 shadow-sm md:grid-cols-[5rem_1fr]\"><span class=\"flex h-16 w-16 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-honey/30 text-2xl font-bold\">4</span><div><h2 class=\"display text-3xl font-bold\">Keep or gift it</h2><p class=\"mt-3 max-w-3xl leading-7 text-ink/72\">Download the finished book, share it with family, or save it for a special bedtime.</p></div></section></div><div class=\"mt-10 rounded-[2rem] border border-line bg-card p-8\"><h2 class=\"display text-2xl font-bold mb-4\">What&#x27;s inside every book</h2><div class=\"grid gap-3 sm:grid-cols-2 text-sm text-ink/70 leading-7\"><div class=\"flex items-start gap-3\"><span class=\"mt-2 h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-honey flex-shrink-0\"></span><span>10 chapters, each with 2 text pages and 2 illustrations</span></div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-3\"><span class=\"mt-2 h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-honey flex-shrink-0\"></span><span>20 custom illustrations in the style you choose</span></div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-3\"><span class=\"mt-2 h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-honey flex-shrink-0\"></span><span>Title page and cover</span></div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-3\"><span class=\"mt-2 h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-honey flex-shrink-0\"></span><span>Dedication page</span></div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-3\"><span class=\"mt-2 h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-hone